yoGiants" target="_blank" rel="noopener">读卖巨人队（Giants）Twitter</a></p><h2>虹山寺四周年演唱会“FANTASIA”纪念服装展</h2><p><a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/07/2-f0b83ff7a48ba67d64c5408f1d8867c9-kix.p9nwsdy8kad9.jpg" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/07/2-f0b83ff7a48ba67d64c5408f1d8867c9-kix.p9nwsdy8kad9.jpg"></a></p><p>为纪念虹山寺出道四周年演唱会“FANTASIA”Blu-ray发行而举办的纪念服装展将于7月25日（星期二）在Animate池袋总店举办。</p><p>在纪念服装展的特别展示空间中，将展示<a href="https://twitter.com/MitoTsukino" target="_blank" rel="noopener">水户月野</a>和<a href="https://twitter.com/Kanae_2434" target="_blank" rel="noopener">卡诺</a>的共同服装。</p><p>此外，在Animate池袋总店6楼的大屏幕上，将于7月24日（周一）至8月14日（周一）期间限时放映现场视频。</p><p> （参考）<a href="https://prtimes.jp/main/html/rd/p/000000660.000030865.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">ANYCOLOR Inc.新闻稿</a></p><h2>Rime x Guiano 专辑《imagine》发行</h2><p><a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/07/3-f0b83ff7a48ba67d64c5408f1d8867c9-kix.l0k8fbmb6k9u.jpg" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/07/3-f0b83ff7a48ba67d64c5408f1d8867c9-kix.l0k8fbmb6k9u.jpg"></a></p><p> <a href="https://twitter.com/kamitsubaki_jp" target="_blank" rel="noopener">KAMITSUBAKI STUDIO</a>的虚拟歌手<a href="https://twitter.com/RIM_virtual" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Rime</a>与创作型歌手<a href="https://twitter.com/GuiAnoDayo" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Guiano</a>的合作专辑《imagine》现已开放预购。</p><p> Guiano负责《imagine》所有原创歌曲的作词、作曲和编曲。</p><p><a href="https://findmestore.thinkr.jp/products/ktr-000-0116" target="_blank" rel="noopener">点击此处</a>进行预订。</p><p> （参考） <a href="https://twitter.com/RIM_virtual" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Rime Twitter</a></p><h2> Hololive 猫又冈汤和犬神可隆迷你人偶</h2><p><a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/07/4-f0b83ff7a48ba67d64c5408f1d8867c9-kix.cha2ty1z13hn.jpg" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/07/4-f0b83ff7a48ba67d64c5408f1d8867c9-ki